<doxygen xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="compound.xsd" version="1.9.8" xml:lang="en-US">
  <compounddef id="group__analysis__module" kind="group">
    <compoundname>analysis_module</compoundname>
    <title>Analysis Module</title>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Central orchestrator for physics analysis workflows. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<sect1 id="group__analysis__module_1analysis_overview">
<title>Overview</title>
<para>The Analysis module contains the main <ref refid="classanalysis" kindref="compound">analysis</ref> class, which serves as the central orchestrator for the entire analysis workflow. It coordinates:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Data loading and sample management</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Event processing and reconstruction</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Selection application</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="classGraph" kindref="compound">Graph</ref> construction</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Model training and inference</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Metric evaluation</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__analysis__module_1analysis_workflow_mod">
<title>Workflow</title>
<para>A typical analysis workflow using the analysis class:</para>
<para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Create an analysis instance</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Add data samples with <computeroutput>add_samples()</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Add event templates with <computeroutput>add_event_template()</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Add graph templates with <computeroutput>add_graph_template()</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Add selection templates with <computeroutput>add_selection_template()</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Add models with <computeroutput>add_model()</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Add metrics with <computeroutput>add_metric_template()</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Configure settings via <computeroutput>m_settings</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Start execution with <computeroutput>start()</computeroutput></para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__analysis__module_1analysis_settings_mod">
<title>Configuration</title>
<para>The analysis class uses the <computeroutput><ref refid="structsettings__t" kindref="compound">settings_t</ref></computeroutput> structure for configuration:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Output directory settings</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Threading configuration</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Cache management</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Training parameters</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classanalysis" kindref="compound">analysis</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="structsettings__t" kindref="compound">settings_t</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
</sect1>
    </detaileddescription>
